      "role": "user",
      "content": "professionals don't really get it though. they just talk about \"managing\" the pain or \"coping mechanisms\" like they're trying to teach me how to enjoy being burned alive. it's not a mental thing, it's just my life. it feels like i'm just waiting for a break that’s never coming. sometimes i look at it and it just feels like there's no point in dragging this out forever.",
